            "title": "1. How can I check the status of my order?",
            "content": "<ul><li>Once your order has been shipped, we will send you an email notification with tracking information. You can use the tracking link to check the order status and the estimated delivery time.</li><li> You can also <a href=\"https://aeststudios.com/tools/order-tracking\" title=\"https://aeststudios.com/tools/order-tracking\">click here</a> to access our Order Tracking Portal. Enter your order number or related details to track your order.</li><li> If no tracking information is available, it may be because your order has just been shipped and the carrier has not yet updated the tracking details. Typically, tracking information will be available within 48 hours of shipping.</li><li>Since our products are high-value items, we recommend carefully checking your package when you received. If you are unsatisfied with the product or notice any issues, please submit a return request as soon as possible so we can provide timely support.</li></ul>"
          }
