            "content": "<ul><li> If you decide to cancel your order, please contact us as soon as possible at hello@aeststudios.com.</li><li> If the order has not yet been shipped, we will do our best to cancel it for you.</li><li>If the order has already been shipped, we will not be able to intercept it. In such cases, you may return the product upon receipt or refuse the delivery.</li><li>If you do not immediately return or refuse the package, you will be responsible for the return shipping fees.</li></ul><p>Noted：</p><ul><li>Please note that some orders cannot be canceled or refunded (e.g., gift cards, customized products, etc.).</li><li>If you have any questions, please contact us at hello@aeststudios.com, and we will work to find a solution.</li></ul>"
